			title: "Primitive Blast Furnace"
			x: -6.5d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["65F2399D1833ECC6"]
			description: ["The Coke Oven is built from 25 Coke Oven Bricks — mixed Clay Ball and Sand into Compressed Coke Clay, fired in a furnace. The structure itself is a 3x3x3 hollow cube. It converts Coal into Coal Coke (twice the fuel value of coal) and produces Creosote Oil as a byproduct. Creosote treats wood planks into Treated Wood — a weather-resistant material used in many GT structures. Coal Coke is the preferred steam boiler fuel at this stage."]
			id: "5C1E8B4D2F7A3E9C"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "F2AE4A9B1C8D5E1B"
				item: "kubejs:coin"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [
