		}
		{
			dependencies: ["8E5F2A9D6C4B1E7C"]
			description: ["The LV Macerator is GregTech's first electric ore processor. It grinds ores into two Crushed Ore pieces — a guaranteed 2x yield — plus a chance at a secondary byproduct dust unique to each ore type. Iron gives a chance at Tin Dust. Gold gives a chance at Copper Dust. Copper gives a chance at Gold Dust. These byproduct dusts accumulate into real material value over time. The Macerator alone exceeds Create's Crushing Wheel output by adding the byproduct chain."]
			id: "2F8A6D3B1E4C9F5D"
